01:15:48.583 --> 01:15:51.540
[Noah] <i>I don't understand.
Ronnie already took your car.</i>

1223
01:15:51.541 --> 01:15:54.332
[Nick] <i>Something
else is going on.</i>

1224
01:15:54.333 --> 01:15:56.124
- [Nick winces]
- [Noah] Sorry.

1225
01:15:56.125 --> 01:15:57.583
It's all right.

1226
01:16:00.625 --> 01:16:02.333
Your touch feels good.

1227
01:16:09.291 --> 01:16:11.083
You know it means strength.

1228
01:16:16.041 --> 01:16:17.707
I get there's a code. whatever.

1229
01:16:17.708 --> 01:16:21.207
but at what point
do we tell someone?

1230
01:16:21.208 --> 01:16:24.540
[Nick] We don't. I'll
deal with Ronnie.

1231
01:16:24.541 --> 01:16:26.583
[Noah] You mean fight him?

1232
01:16:28.708 --> 01:16:30.833
I don't fight anymore.

1233
01:16:31.291 --> 01:16:32.750
Promise.

1234
01:16:35.958 --> 01:16:39.083
Right. let's get some sleep.
Early flight tomorrow.

1235
01:16:39.541 --> 01:16:41.458
And I'm not missing it.

1236
01:16:47.583 --> 01:16:48.582
Thank you.

1237
01:16:48.583 --> 01:16:50.499
So. Nick and Noah.
yeah. are like...?

1238
01:16:50.500 --> 01:16:52.207
- Yeah. Take this.
- I'm baffed.

1239
01:16:52.208 --> 01:16:54.915
- Thank you. Ah. beautiful.
<i>- Gracias. Gracias. señor.</i>

1240
01:16:54.916 --> 01:16:58.165
Noah knows. I know. Nick
doesn't know anyone knows.

1241
01:16:58.166 --> 01:16:59.541
- [Lion] OK.
- So. it's still...

1242
01:17:02.041 --> 01:17:03.540
[Lion] You know
what I want. bruv.

1243
01:17:03.541 --> 01:17:05.165
Move over.

1244
01:17:05.166 --> 01:17:06.875
[Jenna] Do that
again. I dare you.

1245
01:17:07.791 --> 01:17:08.999
[Lion] <i>Pardon.</i> Margarita?

1246
01:17:09.000 --> 01:17:10.582
- Ah. yes!
- Yes.

1247
01:17:10.583 --> 01:17:13.499
- Here you go. here you go.
- Lovely. Thank you.

1248
01:17:13.500 --> 01:17:15.457
Hey. you look. like. cosy.

1249
01:17:15.458 --> 01:17:16.790
- Cosy.
- [Nick] So cosy.

1250
01:17:16.791 --> 01:17:18.665
I might just go jump
in the middle of you.

1251
01:17:18.666 --> 01:17:20.582
Cheers. everyone.

1252
01:17:20.583 --> 01:17:24.165
[Lion] Ibiza. baby.
Let's get messy.

1253
01:17:24.166 --> 01:17:25.624
[Noah] We should get jet skis.

1254
01:17:25.625 --> 01:17:27.707
[Jen exhales] You're such
an adrenaline junkie.

1255
01:17:27.708 --> 01:17:30.040
I wish we could just sit
down for ten minutes. Chill.

1256
01:17:30.041 --> 01:17:33.124
[Noah chuckles] Well then.
I'm just gonna go swim.

1257
01:17:33.125 --> 01:17:35.874
[chuckles] Er. OK. yeah.

1258
01:17:35.875 --> 01:17:37.374
[Jenna] You want me
to come with you?

1259
01:17:37.375 --> 01:17:39.915
[Noah] You don't have
to. but I'd like it.

1260
01:17:39.916 --> 01:17:41.582
- Come on!
- [Lion] Have a little paddle.

1261
01:17:41.583 --> 01:17:44.249
- Yes. yes. yes. yes.
- Have fun. Love you.

1262
01:17:44.250 --> 01:17:46.916
- [Jenna] Yeah. love you.
- Kiss. [chuckles]

1263
01:17:50.875 --> 01:17:52.083
[Lion] Talk to me. bro.

1264
01:17:53.333 --> 01:17:54.415
What?

1265
01:17:54.416 --> 01:17:55.915
What's the sitch
with you and Noah?

1266
01:17:55.916 --> 01:17:58.999
- [scoffs]
- Come. Spill the beans.

1267
01:17:59.000 --> 01:18:00.750
There is no me and Noah.

1268
01:18:01.625 --> 01:18:03.165
Now the problem
with that statement

1269
01:18:03.166 --> 01:18:06.332
is I don't know if you're
lying to me or to yourself.

1270
01:18:06.333 --> 01:18:07.666
Come.

1271
01:18:08.708 --> 01:18:12.457
All right. But let's just
say. for argument's sake.

1272
01:18:12.458 --> 01:18:14.041
there was a "me and Noah".

1273
01:18:16.041 --> 01:18:18.250
Can you imagine how
messy that would be?

1274
01:18:19.291 --> 01:18:24.375
Look. me. personally.
bro. I like messy.

1275
01:18:27.291 --> 01:18:29.624
- [pats leg]
- [both chuckle]

1276
01:18:29.625 --> 01:18:30.916
Look. life. yeah?

1277
01:18:32.000 --> 01:18:33.165
You get one of 'em.

1278
01:18:33.166 --> 01:18:35.582
You gotta do what makes
you happy. all right?

1279
01:18:35.583 --> 01:18:38.207
And you know I got you.
man. no matter what.

1280
01:18:38.208 --> 01:18:41.040
- Feel me?
- I feel you.

1281
01:18:41.041 --> 01:18:44.499
But. now... [Spanish accent]
Let's party. baby. Let's party.

1282
01:18:44.500 --> 01:18:45.915
I wanna get two piña coladas.

1283
01:18:45.916 --> 01:18:48.374
- All right. come.
- Let's go. let's go. let's go!

