1300
01:20:11.875 --> 01:20:14.332
Yo. You good?

1301
01:20:14.333 --> 01:20:15.500
Yeah.

1302
01:20:20.375 --> 01:20:22.250
What are we gonna do
about Ronnie. bro?

1303
01:20:23.000 --> 01:20:27.375
I've heard he's looking for
us. Well. what's the plan?

1304
01:20:28.333 --> 01:20:29.832
I don't know.

1305
01:20:29.833 --> 01:20:33.874
- "I don't know"?
- No. I'm not fighting anymore.

1306
01:20:33.875 --> 01:20:35.291
[Lion] Bro. this ain't a joke!

1307
01:20:35.958 --> 01:20:39.708
That shit you pulled at
the fight. it cost us.

1308
01:20:40.666 --> 01:20:41.958
It cost me.

1309
01:20:43.208 --> 01:20:44.833
I need you to fight him.

1310
01:20:46.916 --> 01:20:48.290
And you gotta let him win.

1311
01:20:48.291 --> 01:20:51.458
Or else we'll always
be watching our backs.

1312
01:20:57.625 --> 01:21:00.124
[Nick] Guess I don't
have a choice. then.

1313
01:21:00.125 --> 01:21:01.583
Yeah.

1314
01:21:28.166 --> 01:21:30.250
Hey. No. no. no.
We're just friends.

1315
01:21:36.750 --> 01:21:38.041
[crowd gasps]

1316
01:21:39.375 --> 01:21:40.791
Nick!

1317
01:21:51.083 --> 01:21:52.708
[cheering]

1318
01:21:54.541 --> 01:21:55.666
Get off me.

1319
01:21:58.375 --> 01:21:59.415
Nick.

1320
01:21:59.416 --> 01:22:01.374
Oi. Nick. What the
hell was that. man?

1321
01:22:01.375 --> 01:22:03.582
He was a creep. Jenna. He
had his hands all over her.

1322
01:22:03.583 --> 01:22:04.915
Bro. she was fine.

1323
01:22:04.916 --> 01:22:06.540
So you thought hitting him
was the right thing to do?

1324
01:22:06.541 --> 01:22:08.499
Yeah. well. it made
<i>me</i> feel better.

1325
01:22:08.500 --> 01:22:10.249
Well. that just about
sums it up. doesn't it?

1326
01:22:10.250 --> 01:22:11.625
It's all about you.

1327
01:22:12.958 --> 01:22:14.082
I'm gonna go see if he's OK.

1328
01:22:14.083 --> 01:22:15.457
Don't you...

1329
01:22:15.458 --> 01:22:18.165
- Nick. Nick. Nick. Nick.
- Babe. Babe. come inside. yeah?

1330
01:22:18.166 --> 01:22:20.625
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm
sorry. I didn't mean that.

1331
01:22:23.041 --> 01:22:26.291
You know. I can't do
this. because of you.

1332
01:22:27.083 --> 01:22:31.125
Because you represent everything
I've been running from.

1333
01:22:32.916 --> 01:22:34.000
[Nick] Noah...

1334
01:22:35.416 --> 01:22:37.208
you know I'd never hurt you.

1335
01:22:40.875 --> 01:22:42.375
You already have.

1336
01:22:44.875 --> 01:22:46.166
[Jenna] Come on. babe.

1337
01:22:47.333 --> 01:22:48.541
Noah!

1338
01:22:51.416 --> 01:22:53.708
[Lion] All right.
man. Let's go home.

1339
01:22:54.916 --> 01:22:56.083
[inhales sharply]

1340
01:22:58.041 --> 01:22:59.333
[exhales]

1341
01:23:50.458 --> 01:23:52.791
[pants]

1342
01:23:54.875 --> 01:23:57.500
[Jenna] <i>You know. I've known
Nick a really long time.</i>

1343
01:23:58.833 --> 01:24:00.957
And. yeah. he can be a little
bit hot-headed sometimes.

1344
01:24:00.958 --> 01:24:04.290
but he's a good guy deep down.

1345
01:24:04.291 --> 01:24:05.916
And he's a really good friend.

1346
01:24:06.750 --> 01:24:09.666
Maybe don't write him
off straight away.

1347
01:24:11.083 --> 01:24:13.416
He's just got weird ways
of showing he cares.

1348
01:24:14.333 --> 01:24:17.457
Come on. man. we're
at a party. Drink up.

1349
01:24:17.458 --> 01:24:19.165
- [laughs]
- Posh party too. babe.

1350
01:24:19.166 --> 01:24:20.624
- Took forever.
- [both laugh]

1351
01:24:20.625 --> 01:24:24.415
- Who invited them?
- Giles did.

1352
01:24:24.416 --> 01:24:27.082
Nick's been MIA ever
since she arrived.

1353
01:24:27.083 --> 01:24:29.249
[girl] She's so pretty. though.

1354
01:24:29.250 --> 01:24:31.332
Are you for real right now?

1355
01:24:31.333 --> 01:24:34.249
She's so bloody
irritating. [scoffs]

1356
01:24:34.250 --> 01:24:37.040
I wish she'd just disappear.

1357
01:24:37.041 --> 01:24:39.540
- [laughs]
- [girl 2] It's your party.

1358
01:24:39.541 --> 01:24:42.166
Maybe we ought to teach
her a little lesson.

1359
01:24:52.500 --> 01:24:54.874
Noah. you don't
need to wait there.

1360
01:24:54.875 --> 01:24:56.624
There's another bathroom
on the top floor.

1361
01:24:56.625 --> 01:24:58.332
- Oh.
- Come on.

1362
01:24:58.333 --> 01:24:59.500
Thanks.

1363
01:25:01.166 --> 01:25:02.250
[door opens]

1364
01:25:14.458 --> 01:25:15.665
[girl 2] Now!

1365
01:25:15.666 --> 01:25:17.332
- [laughter]
- Seriously?!

1366
01:25:17.333 --> 01:25:18.790
- [lock clicks]
- God! [laughs]

1367
01:25:18.791 --> 01:25:19.874
Yes!

1368
01:25:19.875 --> 01:25:22.499
Come on. guys! Really?

1369
01:25:22.500 --> 01:25:24.290
- [exhales] Shit.
- [knocks]

1370
01:25:24.291 --> 01:25:25.665
I'm going to go find Nick.

1371
01:25:25.666 --> 01:25:27.624
- [banging on door]
- [Noah shouts]

1372
01:25:27.625 --> 01:25:30.165
That was so much
fun. [chuckles]

1373
01:25:30.166 --> 01:25:31.375
Shit!

1374
01:25:33.958 --> 01:25:35.041
OK.

1375
01:25:37.625 --> 01:25:38.665
- Good?
- Good. yeah?

1376
01:25:38.666 --> 01:25:40.124
[Jenna] Really good.

1377
01:25:40.125 --> 01:25:41.957
- [Lion] You look good.
- [chuckles]

1378
01:25:41.958 --> 01:25:44.290
- You look beautiful. in fact.
- You look cute.

1379
01:25:44.291 --> 01:25:47.207
- Cute?
- Have you. er. seen Noah?

1380
01:25:47.208 --> 01:25:49.707
Er. I think she went
to the bathroom.

1381
01:25:49.708 --> 01:25:52.583
- You and your little boat shoes.
- Cute.

1382
01:25:54.708 --> 01:25:55.707
Hey. you.

1383
01:25:55.708 --> 01:25:57.665
- Hey.
- You coming for a drink with me?

1384
01:25:57.666 --> 01:25:59.457
Er. yeah. Er...

1385
01:25:59.458 --> 01:26:01.791
- Come on. this way.
- Yeah. all right. OK.

1386
01:26:04.041 --> 01:26:05.125
[exhales sharply]

1387
01:26:12.000 --> 01:26:13.249
[gasps]

1388
01:26:13.250 --> 01:26:16.832
[breathes heavily]

1389
01:26:16.833 --> 01:26:19.000
Help! Help! [sobs]

1390
01:26:19.833 --> 01:26:22.332
I hope you'll be coming to
Bovey Castle next weekend.

1391
01:26:22.333 --> 01:26:23.749
You know the whole gang's going.

1392
01:26:23.750 --> 01:26:26.665
and it's been months since
we've been shooting together.

1393
01:26:26.666 --> 01:26:30.166
- It's always such a laugh.
- Yeah. sure. Maybe.

1394
01:26:31.791 --> 01:26:33.332
Nick. what is going on with you?

1395
01:26:33.333 --> 01:26:35.707
I've barely heard
from you in weeks.

1396
01:26:35.708 --> 01:26:37.624
I'm surprised you even
showed up this evening.

1397
01:26:37.625 --> 01:26:39.625
I've just been busy.

1398
01:26:41.833 --> 01:26:42.958
OK.

1399
01:26:43.708 --> 01:26:44.957
Right. I'm gonna go find Noah.

1400
01:26:44.958 --> 01:26:48.082
Why don't you give your
sister some space. Nick?

1401
01:26:48.083 --> 01:26:50.875
You've been acting weird
ever since she arrived.

1402
01:26:51.708 --> 01:26:54.458
And I've heard a couple
of nasty little rumours.

1403
01:26:55.583 --> 01:26:58.583
God forbid they filter
back to your dad.

1404
01:27:01.000 --> 01:27:02.625
I've just realised something.

1405
01:27:03.458 --> 01:27:05.000
I can't stand you.

1406
01:27:07.083 --> 01:27:08.166
[scoffs]

1407
01:27:11.000 --> 01:27:14.540
[indistinct chatter]

1408
01:27:14.541 --> 01:27:16.458
- OK. fine.
- [laughs]

1409
01:27:17.583 --> 01:27:19.375
Why isn't he with Anna?

1410
01:27:22.750 --> 01:27:24.665
Oh. my God. he's
looking for Noah.

1411
01:27:24.666 --> 01:27:26.124
So embarrassing.

1412
01:27:26.125 --> 01:27:28.458
- Don't say anything.
- [banging on door]

1413
01:27:29.208 --> 01:27:30.582
- [girls snigger]
- [Noah] Help!

1414
01:27:30.583 --> 01:27:31.874
What have you done?

1415
01:27:31.875 --> 01:27:33.915
Noah? Noah?

1416
01:27:33.916 --> 01:27:35.333
Noah?

1417
01:27:37.958 --> 01:27:39.875
- [Nick] Noah!
- [banging on door]

1418
01:27:40.583 --> 01:27:42.082
[man] You're just
like your mother.

1419
01:27:42.083 --> 01:27:43.165
[door handle rattles]

1420
01:27:43.166 --> 01:27:44.999
- No. no! [sobs]
- [Nick] Noah. it's just me.

1421
01:27:45.000 --> 01:27:47.333
Noah! Give me the damn key!

1422
01:27:53.291 --> 01:27:55.250
- [door bangs]
- [Noah screams] No!

1423
01:27:55.833 --> 01:27:57.624
[cries]

1424
01:27:57.625 --> 01:28:00.207
[whimpers]

1425
01:28:00.208 --> 01:28:02.332
[sobs]

1426
01:28:02.333 --> 01:28:04.874
[Nick] Hey. hey. Hey. hey.

1427
01:28:04.875 --> 01:28:08.083
It's just me. It's
just me. It's just me.

1428
01:28:08.750 --> 01:28:10.208
- Hey. it's me.
- [sobs]

1429
01:28:11.375 --> 01:28:13.291
I've got you. I've got you.

1430
01:28:15.000 --> 01:28:16.999
[Noah hyperventilates]

1431
01:28:17.000 --> 01:28:19.750
- Look at me.
- [breathes heavily]

1432
01:28:37.916 --> 01:28:40.958
[Noah] When he was sober.
he was a decent dad.

1433
01:28:44.250 --> 01:28:45.916
Racing was our thing.

1434
01:28:48.250 --> 01:28:51.750
Then his drinking got worse
and he got hooked on oxy.

1435
01:28:56.166 --> 01:28:59.208
You know. I was thinking.
after I met your mom. that...

1436
01:29:00.333 --> 01:29:02.915
if my dad had just sought help.

1437
01:29:02.916 --> 01:29:04.749
you know. like your
mom did. then...

1438
01:29:04.750 --> 01:29:06.958
maybe things would be different.

1439
01:29:11.083 --> 01:29:12.791
He'd never hurt me before.

1440
01:29:20.500 --> 01:29:24.041
Six months after that. I was in
court testifying against him.

1441
01:29:26.375 --> 01:29:28.000
I put my dad in jail.

1442
01:29:43.916 --> 01:29:45.166
Look at me.

1443
01:29:47.916 --> 01:29:49.583
It's not your fault.

1444
01:29:53.250 --> 01:29:54.333
OK?

1445
01:29:55.958 --> 01:29:57.666
None of that is your fault.

1446
01:29:58.833 --> 01:30:00.583
He's just a bad guy.

1447
01:30:03.250 --> 01:30:05.291
And he's one half of me.

1448
01:30:08.041 --> 01:30:09.500
You're not the same.

1449
01:30:12.458 --> 01:30:13.583
It's OK.

1450
01:30:15.541 --> 01:30:17.874
- I'm tough.
- [chuckles]

1451
01:30:17.875 --> 01:30:19.458
Oh. I know!

1452
01:30:24.791 --> 01:30:26.250
You know what I want right now?

1453
01:30:29.166 --> 01:30:30.416
I want you.

1454
01:30:30.958 --> 01:30:32.916
[♪ "Teeth" by Mallrat]

1455
01:30:49.083 --> 01:30:53.749
<i>♪ It's in my hair. in my sleep ♪</i>

1456
01:30:53.750 --> 01:30:57.665
<i>♪ In my hands. in my teeth ♪</i>

1457
01:30:57.666 --> 01:31:01.790
<i>♪ It's in my chair.
it looks like me ♪</i>

1458
01:31:01.791 --> 01:31:06.332
<i>♪ And when it stands.
I take my seat ♪</i>

1459
01:31:06.333 --> 01:31:10.957
<i>♪ It's in the air
