<i>♪ And I'm ready to dive ♪</i>

1526
01:35:20.333 --> 01:35:23.249
<i>♪ Right into you ♪</i>

1527
01:35:23.250 --> 01:35:25.624
<i>♪ I'm ready to dive ♪</i>

1528
01:35:25.625 --> 01:35:28.957
<i>♪ Right into you ♪</i>

1529
01:35:28.958 --> 01:35:32.249
<i>♪ Maybe it's the fact
that every time I fall ♪</i>

1530
01:35:32.250 --> 01:35:34.957
<i>♪ I lose it all ♪</i>

1531
01:35:34.958 --> 01:35:39.040
<i>♪ But you got me from
my head to my feet ♪</i>

1532
01:35:39.041 --> 01:35:43.665
<i>♪ And I'm ready to dive ♪</i>

1533
01:35:43.666 --> 01:35:47.750
[car alarm blares]

1534
01:35:48.791 --> 01:35:52.125
[alarm continues]

1535
01:36:04.666 --> 01:36:07.165
Lion? Lion. you with me. mate?

1536
01:36:07.166 --> 01:36:08.249
[grunts]

1537
01:36:08.250 --> 01:36:09.874
It's gonna be all right. OK?

1538
01:36:09.875 --> 01:36:12.290
[indistinct radio chatter]

1539
01:36:12.291 --> 01:36:14.582
[Jenna] Lion! Well. where
is he? Is he in there?

1540
01:36:14.583 --> 01:36:16.499
- [Nick] Yeah. he's in there.
- What happened?

1541
01:36:16.500 --> 01:36:17.707
- What's happened?
- It's OK.

1542
01:36:17.708 --> 01:36:19.457
He warned you and
you didn't listen.

1543
01:36:19.458 --> 01:36:21.415
- I need to see him.
- I'm sorry.

1544
01:36:21.416 --> 01:36:23.124
- Are you his girlfriend?
- Yeah. yeah.

1545
01:36:23.125 --> 01:36:24.540
- Go and take a seat.
- Are you OK?

1546
01:36:24.541 --> 01:36:26.374
- Dad. I need to tell you...
- Nick. not now.

1547
01:36:26.375 --> 01:36:28.750
- No. but I need to.
- Not now.

1548
01:36:30.375 --> 01:36:33.291
Security are taking Ella and
Noah to a hotel for a few days.

1549
01:36:34.083 --> 01:36:35.500
It's not safe here.

1550
