William's talking to the
police. we've got security.

1563
01:37:31.875 --> 01:37:36.625
Yeah. I know. I just... I
wanna wait for an update. OK?

1564
01:37:37.958 --> 01:37:39.458
Meet me downstairs.

1565
01:37:43.000 --> 01:37:44.415
- [sighs]
- [door closes]

1566
01:37:44.416 --> 01:37:45.790
[Nick] <i>This is Ronnie Burns.</i>

1567
01:37:45.791 --> 01:37:47.957
He took my McLaren when
I refused to fight.

1568
01:37:47.958 --> 01:37:51.040
He smashed up my
car. He beat up Lion.

1569
01:37:51.041 --> 01:37:53.749
He said he'd hurt my friends
if I didn't fight him again.

1570
01:37:53.750 --> 01:37:54.832
What aren't you getting?

1571
01:37:54.833 --> 01:37:58.833
Nick. we believe
Lion's attack...

1572
01:37:59.750 --> 01:38:01.958
was down to Noah's father.

1573
01:38:02.583 --> 01:38:03.833
Travis McKay.

1574
01:38:05.041 --> 01:38:07.832
[scoffs] Sorry. what?

1575
01:38:07.833 --> 01:38:09.915
He's out of jail and in the UK.

1576
01:38:09.916 --> 01:38:13.624
What? No. It's Ronnie.
Ronnie Burns. You know him.

1577
01:38:13.625 --> 01:38:15.458
Yeah. we know Ronnie.

1578
01:38:16.125 --> 01:38:19.208
And he's working for Noah's
father. Travis McKay.

1579
01:38:22.291 --> 01:38:23.958
[Nick] That's Noah's dad?

1580
01:38:24.666 --> 01:38:26.250
I've seen him before.

1581
01:38:27.625 --> 01:38:29.125
<i>He was at the fight and the...</i>

1582
01:38:30.000 --> 01:38:31.332
<i>and the petrol station.</i>

1583
01:38:31.333 --> 01:38:33.207
He's very dangerous. Nick.

1584
01:38:33.208 --> 01:38:35.749
Four years ago.
he attacked Noah.

1585
01:38:35.750 --> 01:38:37.165
That's how she got the scar.

1586
01:38:37.166 --> 01:38:40.333
He was released a few weeks
ago and violated his parole.

1587
01:38:41.500 --> 01:38:43.124
Travelled in on a
stolen passport.

1588
01:38:43.125 --> 01:38:46.207
- And then hired Ronnie?
- Mm-hmm. Right.

1589
01:38:46.208 --> 01:38:48.749
- [Nick] What do they want?
- Probably money.

1590
01:38:48.750 --> 01:38:50.166
Well. what's their play?

1591
01:38:50.875 --> 01:38:52.125
Nick...

1592
01:38:54.250 --> 01:38:55.291
Noah.

1593
01:38:56.750 --> 01:38:58.790
[Nick] <i>When they attacked
us in the car. they...</i>

1594
01:38:58.791 --> 01:39:00.290
<i>they went for Noah's door.</i>

1595
01:39:00.291 --> 01:39:01.832
<i>I thought they were
trying to go for me.</i>

1596
01:39:01.833 --> 01:39:03.332
<i>but they must've
been going for Noah.</i>

1597
01:39:03.333 --> 01:39:05.332
Oh. my God. they left
Lion here to scare us.

1598
01:39:05.333 --> 01:39:07.790
They were smoking us
out and we've just...

1599
01:39:07.791 --> 01:39:09.875
we've just played
straight into their hands.

1600
01:39:14.750 --> 01:39:16.375
I need to call her.

1601
01:39:20.916 --> 01:39:22.958
[lift whirs]

1602
01:39:36.750 --> 01:39:38.500
[doors close]

1603
01:39:43.666 --> 01:39:45.083
Hello. Noah.

1604
01:39:46.708 --> 01:39:48.540
Can I squeeze in with
you? Is that all right?

1605
01:39:48.541 --> 01:39:49.958
Oh. thank you.

1606
01:39:50.791 --> 01:39:52.666
So. where shall we go?

1607
01:39:53.708 --> 01:39:55.291
[automated voice] <i>Going down.</i>

1608
01:40:02.458 --> 01:40:04.250
I really hope you
like surprises.

1609
01:40:05.166 --> 01:40:06.999
Cos I love surprises.

1610
01:40:07.000 --> 01:40:08.208
[chuckles]

1611
01:40:17.041 --> 01:40:19.250
[breathes shakily]

1612
01:40:20.416 --> 01:40:22.875
[exhales] Hi. kid.

1613
01:40:25.125 --> 01:40:28.624
- Go to Daddy. Go. go. go. go.
- [whimpers]

1614
01:40:28.625 --> 01:40:31.749
[over police radio] <i>Code 134.
A missing 18-year-old female.</i>

1615
01:40:31.750 --> 01:40:32.874
<i>All units be on alert...</i>

1616
01:40:32.875 --> 01:40:34.332
[Sato] We're checking the hotel.

1617
01:40:34.333 --> 01:40:36.290
You're checking the hotel? No.
you're not. you're sat there.

1618
01:40:36.291 --> 01:40:38.082
There's one. two. three. four.
five of you and she's out there.

1619
01:40:38.083 --> 01:40:39.999
- and you lot are just sat there.
- Oi. Oi. oi. oi.

1620
01:40:40.000 --> 01:40:42.415
[phone vibrates]

1621
01:40:42.416 --> 01:40:43.750
[Sato] You need to get that.

1622
01:40:48.791 --> 01:40:50.790
This is William Leister.

1623
01:40:50.791 --> 01:40:52.749
Am I speaking with Travis?

1624
01:40:52.750 --> 01:40:55.582
<i>Yeah. you're
speaking with Travis.</i>

1625
01:40:55.583 --> 01:40:58.207
[William] <i>We want
to speak to Noah.</i>

1626
01:40:58.208 --> 01:40:59.916
I thought you might.

1627
01:41:02.708 --> 01:41:04.207
[whimpers] Nick!

1628
01:41:04.208 --> 01:41:05.540
<i>- Nick. help!</i>
- Noah. hey. hey.

1629
01:41:05.541 --> 01:41:07.207
- Tell us where you are.
- Help. Nick! Help!

1630
01:41:07.208 --> 01:41:08.290
- Nick!
<i>- I'll find you.</i>

1631
01:41:08.291 --> 01:41:09.915
Please.

1632
01:41:09.916 --> 01:41:12.332
<i>- What do you want?</i>
- A million.

1633
01:41:12.333 --> 01:41:15.041
<i>- Wire it to this account.</i>
- [phone vibrates]

1634
01:41:16.166 --> 01:41:18.125
<i>- Come on. I know you got it.</i>
- I'll get it.

1635
01:41:18.583 --> 01:41:20.290
- Please.
<i>- You have one hour.</i>

1636
01:41:20.291 --> 01:41:21.582
[William] Don't hurt her.

1637
01:41:21.583 --> 01:41:23.665
You send the cash.
the kid'll be fine.

1638
01:41:23.666 --> 01:41:25.957
- I want what's best for Noah.
- Dad. please.

1639
01:41:25.958 --> 01:41:27.916
- [Noah] <i>Help!</i>
- [phone beeps]

1640
01:41:28.916 --> 01:41:30.166
He's gone.

1641
01:41:40.458 --> 01:41:41.915
What did I say about
smoking that shit?

1642
01:41:41.916 --> 01:41:43.500
It's not good for you.

1643
01:41:47.416 --> 01:41:49.625
Stupid. stupid. stupid!

1644
01:41:51.416 --> 01:41:53.125
[exhales shakily]

1645
01:42:10.375 --> 01:42:11.957
[tyres screech]

1646
01:42:11.958 --> 01:42:14.290
- Dad. I've got something.
- [William] <i>Nick. where are you?</i>

1647
01:42:14.291 --> 01:42:16.540
Ronnie has my McLaren. My
McLaren has a tracker in it.

1648
01:42:16.541 --> 01:42:18.374
If I can find the McLaren.
I can find Ronnie.

1649
01:42:18.375 --> 01:42:19.749
If I find Ronnie.
I can find Noah.

1650
01:42:19.750 --> 01:42:21.999
<i>Nick. I'll tell the police. but
you have to let them handle it.</i>

1651
01:42:22.000 --> 01:42:23.582
- Oh. shit!
- [tyres screech]

1652
01:42:23.583 --> 01:42:24.915
[Nick] I'll send
you the address.

1653
01:42:24.916 --> 01:42:26.500
Get the police to follow me.

1654
01:42:29.625 --> 01:42:31.832
[Noah whimpers]

1655
01:42:31.833 --> 01:42:33.499
[loud clang]

1656
01:42:33.500 --> 01:42:35.166
[Ronnie] Hello. Noah.

1657
01:42:36.500 --> 01:42:38.916
How's it going. love? You
all right? [clears throat]

1658
01:42:39.833 --> 01:42:41.333
You being looked after?

1659
01:42:43.041 --> 01:42:44.166
So...

1660
01:42:44.875 --> 01:42:46.915
as you've heard.
the plan. right.

1661
01:42:46.916 --> 01:42:48.625
is to swap you out for the cash.

1662
01:42:49.750 --> 01:42:50.833
Piece of piss.

1663
01:42:51.791 --> 01:42:53.791
But I just wanted to let
you in on a little secret.

1664
01:42:54.791 --> 01:42:56.791
I'm not really
interested in the money.

1665
01:42:57.541 --> 01:43:00.583
[laughs] I want to
eat the rich! But...

1666
01:43:01.958 --> 01:43:04.082
Here's my logic. OK? I'm
gonna share this with you

1667
01:43:04.083 --> 01:43:07.249
because I think we're gonna
see eye to eye with this.

1668
01:43:07.250 --> 01:43:09.040
I get locked up trying
to graft a living.

1669
01:43:09.041 --> 01:43:10.790
while the Nicks of the
world breeze through.

1670
01:43:10.791 --> 01:43:12.374
Now. is that fair?

1671
01:43:12.375 --> 01:43:14.124
- [grunts]
- [clattering]

1672
01:43:14.125 --> 01:43:17.833
Nick thinks he's a hero. and
what do heroes always do?

1673
01:43:21.750 --> 01:43:23.165
- [clicks fingers]
- That's it.

1674
01:43:23.166 --> 01:43:26.124
Save the girl. You're my bait.

1675
01:43:26.125 --> 01:43:29.625
- [claps]
- Oh. Nicky's gonna be so sad!

1676
01:43:31.208 --> 01:43:33.040
So sad he didn't get
to say goodbye to ya.

1677
01:43:33.041 --> 01:43:34.540
Well. it's tragic. really.

1678
01:43:34.541 --> 01:43:37.250
[Noah sobs]

1679
01:43:40.666 --> 01:43:42.540
Did you really think

1680
01:43:42.541 --> 01:43:45.625
I was gonna let Nick walk
away from another fight?

1681
01:43:52.916 --> 01:43:54.625
Where've you been?

1682
01:43:55.000 --> 01:43:56.540
[grunts]

1683
01:43:56.541 --> 01:43:58.791
I was just making sure
the package is secure.

1684
01:44:00.541 --> 01:44:01.875
You don't talk to her.

1685
01:44:02.500 --> 01:44:03.958
Didn't say a word to her. mate.

1686
01:44:04.750 --> 01:44:08.790
[sobs]

1687
01:44:08.791 --> 01:44:10.875
[engine roars]

1688
01:44:12.666 --> 01:44:15.166
[man] Shit. We have a visitor.

1689
01:44:16.208 --> 01:44:17.833
What... what visitor?

1690
01:44:20.125 --> 01:44:22.249
- Get Noah.
- How many are there?

1691
01:44:22.250 --> 01:44:23.625
It's just Nick.

1692
01:44:24.750 --> 01:44:26.416
[Travis] The cops
won't be far behind.

1693
01:44:27.625 --> 01:44:28.791
